0 -12 Td
(2. Prepare the machine) Tj
0 -12 Td
() Tj
0 -12 Td
(   Use a bare-metal machine with Ubuntu 24.04+ or the currently recommended) Tj
0 -12 Td
(   Linux version. Update the system, then reboot if a kernel update was) Tj
0 -12 Td
(   installed.) Tj
0 -12 Td
() Tj
0 -12 Td
