0 -12 Td
() Tj
0 -12 Td
(3. Disable SMT/HyperThreading) Tj
0 -12 Td
() Tj
0 -12 Td
(   Monad's official docs recommend disabling SMT/HT for more predictable node) Tj
0 -12 Td
(   performance. On most mini-PCs this is done in BIOS/UEFI. After rebooting,) Tj
0 -12 Td
(   check:) Tj
0 -12 Td
() Tj
0 -12 Td
(       lscpu) Tj
0 -12 Td
() Tj
0 -12 Td
