0 -12 Td
() Tj
0 -12 Td
(   The node signs a name record so peers can discover it. The official docs show) Tj
0 -12 Td
(   the `monad-sign-name-record` command. After generating the record, update) Tj
0 -12 Td
(   the `peer_discovery` section in `node.toml`.) Tj
0 -12 Td
() Tj
0 -12 Td
(   Privacy warning: do not post this section publicly without redacting network) Tj
0 -12 Td
(   address data and signatures.) Tj
0 -12 Td
() Tj
0 -12 Td
